net-snmp (5.9.1+dfsg-1ubuntu2.7) jammy; urgency=medium

  * d/patches: apply patch set to fix segfault caused by use after free.
    (LP: #720638)
    - d/p/pass-nw-if.patch: pass network interface index to
      netsnmp_access_interface_entry_create.
    - d/p/fix-memory-leak.patch: fix possible memory leak when reading network
      interfaces.
    - d/p/fix-if-race-cond.patch: fix race condition when scanning network
      interfaces.
    - d/p/fix-use-after-free.patch: fix use after free.

 -- Athos Ribeiro <athos.ribeiro@canonical.com>  Tue, 27 Aug 2024 20:20:43 -0300

