  * Fix snmptrapd reconnection issue after hitting MySQL wait_timeout
    (LP: #1999711)
    - d/p/snmptrapd-mysql-reconnection-after-hitting-wait_timeout.patch
    - d/p/snmptrapd-mysql-fix-build-error.patch

